snippet.title: Returnal - Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the intense launch trailer for Returnal for another look at the game, enemies, and more.

Take on the hostiles of Atropos as Selene and uncover hidden secrets while trapped in a chaotic time loop when Return arrives on April 30, 2021, on PlayStation 5.

#IGN #Gaming #PS5
